title: 3 Bedroom 2 Bath Home
posting_body: ['Property located in quiet Hillside neighborhood of Daly City near San Bruno Mountain and County Park.', 'Traditional tunnel entry, 3 bedroom 2 bath, living room w/fireplace, updated kitchen with new appliances with a small nook and separate dining area.', 'Hardwood floors.', 'Washer/Dryer.', 'Huge bonus room downstairs with a separate storage room, small functioning bathroom with shower.', 'Accessible from entrance or via garage, upstairs or back door from the backyard.', 'Low maintenance backyard.', 'Tenants responsible for all utilities and upkeep of backyard/front yard.', 'Nearby schools: Susan B Anthony Elementary K-5, Thomas R. Pollicita Middle School 6-8, Jefferson High School 9-12', 'Near BART and bus route Samtrans 130', 'Move in requirements: Current ID/Passport, 3 most current pay stubs, 2 mos bank statements, bring current credit/background check or $45 non-refundable fee to run credit/background check, rental application and references.', 'It’s Month’s Rent:$4000.00', 'Deposit: $6000.00', 'Available 9/1 or late August', 'Inquiries: TEXT or email  and by appointment only.']
